### **PEP 8 Compliance**
- **Line Length**: Maximum 79 characters
- **Indentation**: 4 spaces (no tabs)
- **Naming**: snake_case for variables/functions, PascalCase for classes
- **Imports**: Group imports (standard library, third-party, local)

